@startuml SD_10_Chat
' ============================================================
' SEQUENCE DIAGRAM - Live Chat
' FR-29~FR-30: Customer ↔ Organizer Chat
' ============================================================

title **SD-10: Live Chat\n(Customer ↔ Organizer Real-time Messaging)**

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam sequence {
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #E0F7FA
    ParticipantBorderColor #00838F
    ArrowColor #00838F
}

actor "Attendee" as Customer #LightBlue
participant "Customer\nBrowser" as CBrowser #LightYellow
participant "ChatServlet\n(API)" as Controller #E0F7FA
participant "ChatService" as Service #E8F5E9
participant "ChatDAO" as DAO #FFF3E0
database "SQL Server" as DB #F3E5F5
participant "Organizer\nBrowser" as OBrowser #FFFDE7
actor "Organizer" as Organizer #Gold

== Step 1: Open Chat ==

Customer -> CBrowser: Click "Chat with Organizer"\non event page
CBrowser -> Controller: POST /api/chat/sessions\n{eventId, organizerId}
activate Controller
Controller -> Service: getOrCreateSession(\ncustomerId, eventId, organizerId)
activate Service
Service -> DAO: findSession(\ncustomerId, eventId, organizerId)
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: SELECT * FROM ChatSessions\nWHERE customerId = ?\nAND eventId = ?\nAND organizerId = ?
activate DB
DB --> DAO: Session or null
deactivate DB
DAO --> Service: session
deactivate DAO

alt Session not found
    Service -> DAO: create(ChatSession)
    activate DAO
    DAO -> DB: INSERT INTO ChatSessions\n(sessionId, customerId,\neventId, organizerId,\nstatus='active', createdAt)
    activate DB
    DB --> DAO: sessionId
    deactivate DB
    DAO --> Service: new session
    deactivate DAO

    Service -> DB: INSERT Notifications\n(userId=organizerId,\ntype='NEW_CHAT',\nmessage='New chat from\n{customerName} about\nevent {title}')
end

Service --> Controller: ChatSession
deactivate Service
Controller --> CBrowser: JSON {sessionId,\nmessages: []}
deactivate Controller
CBrowser --> Customer: 💬 Chat window opens

== Step 2: Send Message (Customer) ==

Customer -> CBrowser: Type message +\nClick Send
CBrowser -> Controller: POST /api/chat/messages\n{sessionId, content:\n"When does the event start?"}
activate Controller
Controller -> Service: sendMessage(\nsessionId, senderId,\ncontent, senderRole)
activate Service
Service -> DAO: createMessage(message)
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: INSERT INTO ChatMessages\n(messageId, sessionId,\nsenderId, senderRole='customer',\ncontent, createdAt)
activate DB
DB --> DAO: messageId
deactivate DB
DAO --> Service: OK
deactivate DAO

Service -> DAO: updateSession(sessionId)
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: UPDATE ChatSessions SET\nlastMessageAt = GETDATE()
DAO --> Service: OK
deactivate DAO

Service -> DB: INSERT Notifications\n(userId=organizerId,\ntype='NEW_MESSAGE')

Service --> Controller: message (created)
deactivate Service
Controller --> CBrowser: JSON {messageId,\ntimestamp, status: "sent"}
deactivate Controller
CBrowser --> Customer: ✅ Message sent

== Step 3: Organizer Receives (Polling) ==

note over OBrowser
  JavaScript polls every 3s
  for new messages
end note

OBrowser -> Controller: GET /api/chat/messages\n?sessionId={id}\n&after={lastTimestamp}
activate Controller
Controller -> Service: getMessages(sessionId,\nafter)
activate Service
Service -> DAO: findNewMessages(\nsessionId, after)
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: SELECT * FROM ChatMessages\nWHERE sessionId = ?\nAND createdAt > ?\nORDER BY createdAt
activate DB
DB --> DAO: new messages
deactivate DB
DAO --> Service: messages
deactivate DAO
Service --> Controller: messages
deactivate Service
Controller --> OBrowser: JSON {messages: [\n  {sender: "Customer",\n   content: "When does the\n   event start?",\n   time: "14:30"}\n]}
deactivate Controller
OBrowser --> Organizer: 💬 New message:\n"When does the event start?"

== Step 4: Organizer Replies ==

Organizer -> OBrowser: Type reply + Send
OBrowser -> Controller: POST /api/chat/messages\n{sessionId, content:\n"The event starts at 7 PM,\nNov 3rd. See you there!"}
activate Controller
Controller -> Service: sendMessage(...)
activate Service
Service -> DAO: createMessage(message)
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: INSERT INTO ChatMessages\n(senderRole='organizer', ...)
activate DB
DB --> DAO: OK
deactivate DB
DAO --> Service: OK
deactivate DAO

Service -> DB: INSERT Notifications\n(userId=customerId,\ntype='NEW_MESSAGE')

Service --> Controller: message
deactivate Service
Controller --> OBrowser: JSON {success: true}
deactivate Controller
OBrowser --> Organizer: ✅ Reply sent

' --- Customer receives via polling ---
CBrowser -> Controller: GET /api/chat/messages\n?sessionId={id}&after=...
activate Controller
Controller --> CBrowser: JSON {messages: [\n  {...organizer's reply...}\n]}
deactivate Controller
CBrowser --> Customer: 💬 Organizer:\n"The event starts at 7 PM,\nNov 3rd. See you there!"

@enduml
